com.intel.icecp.icecp_module_mqttbridge

Class MqttWorkerRunnable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.icecp.icecp_module_mqttbridge.MqttWorkerRunnable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, org.eclipse.paho.client.mqttv3.MqttCallback

    public class MqttWorkerRunnable
extends Object
implements Runnable, org.eclipse.paho.client.mqttv3.MqttCallback
    The MQTT Worker Runnable handles the bridge connections.

    This runnable is responsible for connecting the endpoints for a connectionID. It connects MQTT topics to channels and vice versus. When a connect command is received by the module, it hands the connection information to this runnable. When the start flag of the connect MQTTConnectMessage command is set to true, then the actual connections are made.
